This project is an End to End Encryption Forwarder for linux servers.
This project is only tested on 1 debian server build.
This project is a boddged together project that needs a lot of improvement.
This project is a requires lowering the security of a (hopefully throwaway)gmail account to work using gmail (and probably other email providers). 
SEE: https://myaccount.google.com/lesssecureapps
This project bypasses most of the normal processes of postfix and emails everything to 1 email address.

To read emails sent from this forwarder or for general emailing 
properly configure and use one applications listed here:

https://www.openpgp.org/software/


